Has it sunk in yet? It's thanks to
your support that the people here have
grown so happy and full of life.

rows.label: tlk70000020_05_msg0002
rows.name:
More than individual efforts, your
presence has given us all a valuable
sense of security.

rows.label: tlk70000020_05_msg0003

I'm excited to see what the future
holds for the Iiran people!
